Start the program
Define a structure to store book details like book id,book namw,author name,and quantity
Create an array to store the book records
Display the menu options(Add Book,Display Books,Search Book,Issue Book,Return Book,Exit)
Read the user's choice
If the user selects Add Book,enter the book details and store them
If the user selects Display Books,show all the book records
If the user selects Search Book,enter the book id and display the book details if found
If the user selects Issue Book,reduce the quantity of the book if it is available
If the user selects Return Book,increase the quantity of the book
If the user selects Exit,terminate the program
Stop the program
